==GroupHug the game==
GroupHug.us has spawned a game using its pages. Directions:
#Prima hits the [[Special:Randompage|random button]] on GroupHug and scours the page for the weirdest/[[lulz]]iest/[[wtf]]ist definition on the page.
#Secunda also hits random page and sees if she can out weird/lol/wtf Prima using only that page.
#Prima hits random again and sees if he can top Secunda's ante.
#Secunda hits random again and sees that she cannot beat out Prima. The score is now 1-0 Prima and Secunda submits the best entry on her page to begin the next round.
#Can be played with 2 or more players. If played with more than 2 then each round is played elimination style until a winner of the point is chosen.
#If on IRC in groups: @'s are players still in for the round, +'s are for players sitting out, players who are out for the round have no channel mode.
#If an entry is agreed by a majority of players to be fake, it is DQ'd and another entry must be chosen.
#'''One entry per random page, no more no less.'''
#Play continues until players get bored.
#Alcohol optional.
#????
#PROFIT!

